sub_title: Professor of Cardiology at Maastricht University Medical Centre
summary: Heart failure specialist with broad clinical experience in cardiology. Special interest and experience in personalized care and eHealth. Skilled in clinical research with focus on biomarker and eHealth in heart failure, statistical data analysis, healthcare management, and healthcare. Leader of an international project on eHealth with the aim to develop a physician avatar.
